                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910413-54-off303 t17910413-54-cd304"></join>, two linen sheets, value 8 s. two curtains, value 8 s. a copper tea-kettle, value 18 d. the goods of 
                     
